{"tid":535404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡邨食水疑含藍白色顆粒　一捽變粉究竟係乜？","createTime":"2018-01-20T19:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T07:05:46.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9ea8ae0bb98b6edf2b3d7adf77fa744ed94f4d","tid":535404,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T19:58:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516428576_6d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516428576_6d9e.jpg&h=c39b9568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">黃碧雲接獲居民投訴，指發現水龍頭隔網有藍白色顆粒出現。</span><br />\n<br />\n受鉛水事件困擾3年的紅磡邨居民，再受食水問題困擾。民主黨黃碧雲議員辦事處周四接獲居民投訴，指近期發現水龍頭出水變慢，拆開水龍頭隔網後，發現有藍白色顆粒出現。民主黨遂於邨內3幢樓宇，抽樣向24個不同樓層單位視察，發現21個單位水龍頭，拆開後濾網同樣有顆粒積聚，嚴重程度各有不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516428614_b664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516428614_b664.jpg&h=79cbc5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">紅磡邨受鉛水問題困擾足足3年。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57731549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57731549&d=aPFDXfxti3LQ%2Bk6ZABIzW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=89657e9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57731549&h=ee6457d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57731549</a></div>"},{"pid":"5cbb1f0a60a362acae2fa6ad0d67c4b6d0745740","tid":535404,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T19:58:29.000Z","msg":"民主黨社區主任周熙雯指，有關單位大約於去年11至12月完成換喉，較早換喉單位出現的顆粒相對輕微。顆粒用手擠壓後，會壓碎成藍色粉末。她指，發現問題後，已通知水務署跟進，水務署人員已再到另外4個單位抽取顆粒進行化驗，現正等待化驗結果。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲說，據水務署今早反映，初步化驗結果顆粒為銅鹽，相信是由銅喉釋出的物質與水的化學作用而成，暫時水署仍要與房署研究，究竟是因銅喉內壁抑或是焊料內含銅，以致有關問題出現。黃又引述水務署指，抽取的水辦化驗結果顯示，所有水樣本的含銅量均低於世衞水平，而街喉及天台水箱樣本均未有發現顆粒，相信問題與新更換的喉管有關。她促相關部門盡快查清問題成因，又建議其他受鉛水問題影響屋邨邨民留意問題。"},{"pid":"d4c1db75ea17cad787f9d55136e9b0e3527bee61","tid":535404,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T19:58:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">居住於紅昕樓高層單位的羅婆婆指，自鉛水事件發生後，一直只敢用家中水龍頭清潔家居及洗菜。她說，邨內再次出現食水問題，擔心水中雜質會影響健康，在查清問題前，只會裝起水，待雜質沉澱後再用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516428581_875c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516428581_875c.jpg&h=c872cb18&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a363f654ad7b6d910e13c8e3de15207dfe30ec5d","tid":535404,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"水務署表示，就紅磡邨有用戶的食水龍頭隔篩內發現有藍白色顆粒的事件，在昨日下午收到有關報告後已隨即派員前往該邨調查。調查顯示水務署的供水及在屋邨的儲水箱內均沒有藍白色顆粒，署方同時亦在有關單位收集了顆粒和水樣本，經化驗後證實為銅氧化物（copper salts）。<br />\n<br />\n水務署指出，水樣本測試結果顯示食水樣本的銅含量符合香港食水標準（香港食水標準是根據世界衞生組織《飲用水水質準則》訂定），可以安全飲用。而於食水龍頭隔篩內發現的微量銅氧化物，則不會對食水安全構成影響。水務署表示該銅氧化物相信是來自銅喉或銅合金配件，並承示會與房屋署進一步跟進。<br />\n<br />\n房委會發言人回應指，正如水務署回覆，屋邨內的食水可以安全飲用，而在食水龍頭隔篩內發現的微量銅氧化物，亦不會對食水安全構成影響。房委會提醒水龍頭隔篩應定期清洗但不應除掉，並表示會繼續與水務署保持聯繫，作出適當的跟進。"},{"pid":"86d3faa3deb5a9fd24517ef4453c4d0d5444bf34","tid":535404,"uid":18395,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T01:23:28.000Z","msg":"有毒無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25ed70714dabe63815baa95c56a9f82c175f937","tid":535404,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0529e0ced6f1c454cb121484cba3dac9f3b784de","tid":535404,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864d13e1552b2f125796c79e40c421801bb2d171","tid":535404,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d907350510747c8725f024a73783f523c2a5ee53","tid":535404,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"我屋企拆開都係銹漬"},{"pid":"6c4516558953233e41435b8696662d0819869f5b","tid":535404,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"即場開LIVE沖水飲撚左佢<br />\n有咩事政府包底養過世"},{"pid":"5b5c5c3fc5c8e682f86ed35448ca5a1e652c7fe0","tid":535404,"uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"Cu2+"},{"pid":"d87d5f43b4356622f3e4a1cfd120377b811543a4","tid":535404,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"慢性銅中毒"},{"pid":"708a31f52b1678bdbdd3eb90d0638d04109d42c8","tid":535404,"uid":144774,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wVXQQcU7N8A/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FwVXQQcU7N8A%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=95350a8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9acdaec42a2975e939ceb3fb7f9f06d21f9f71b8","tid":535404,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"藍泡泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed5e10bf0eb7b70bae28d8f7eb465f9888468d8","tid":535404,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"白色珍珠呀"},{"pid":"3e206fd5f142797bbceec1febce3a6ca0bec68be","tid":535404,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"多謝民賤聯啦"}]}